lenders.name: Eric Gerster
lenders.loan_because: I am fortunate enough to have a wonderful family and want to give back in every way possible.
lenders.occupational_info: Eric Gerster began mentoring underprivileged kids in 1993. Since then, he and his wife Mini Nunna have volunteered and served on the board at several different organizations that support those in need both in their community and around the world. Some of the organizations they have supported are: Graham Windham, AmeriCares, and Robin Hood.
